( SELECT way,place, TRANSLATE(UPPER(name), 'àáâãäåæçèéêëìíîïñòóôõöùúûüý', 'ÀÁÂÃÄÅÆÇÈÉÊËÌÍÎÏÑÒÓÔÕÖÙÚÛÜÝ' ) AS name FROM planet_osm_point WHERE "place" IN ('country','state') ORDER BY z_order asc ) AS place_big
( SELECT way,place,name FROM planet_osm_point WHERE "place" IN ('metropolis','city','large_town','town','small_town') ORDER BY z_order asc ) AS placename
( SELECT way,place,name FROM planet_osm_point WHERE "place" IN ('large_village','village','hamlet','suburb','locality','island') ORDER BY z_order asc ) AS placename
( SELECT *, CHAR_LENGTH(ref) AS length FROM planet_osm_line WHERE "highway" IS NOT NULL ORDER BY z_order asc ) AS route_label
( SELECT * FROM planet_osm_point WHERE "amenity" IS NOT NULL ORDER BY z_order asc ) AS amenity
( SELECT * FROM planet_osm_point WHERE "leisure" IN ('garden','playground') ORDER BY z_order asc ) AS iom_leisure
( SELECT * FROM planet_osm_point WHERE "amenity" IN ('bar','cafe','drinking_water','doctors','place_of_worship','restaurant','shower','toilets','waste_basket') ORDER BY z_order asc ) AS iom_amenity
( SELECT * FROM planet_osm_point WHERE "shop" IN ('convenience','beverages','florist') ORDER BY z_order asc ) AS iom_shop
( SELECT way,aeroway,name FROM planet_osm_point WHERE "aeroway" IN ('aerodrome','helipad') ORDER BY z_order asc ) AS airport
( SELECT way,aeroway,name FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE "aeroway" IN ('aerodrome','helipad') ORDER BY z_order asc ) AS airport
